{"tid":979289,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［華為］華為波蘭銷售總監王偉晶被捕 華為：決定中止雇傭關係","createTime":"2019-01-12T14:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T21:28:24.000Z","uid":123082,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"09c9f19413a54c01173ff90b06e61424dc349a8f","tid":979289,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T14:49:22.000Z","msg":"（更新：內容）<span style=\"color: red;\">波蘭當局拘捕華為波蘭銷售總監王偉晶</span>，指他與波蘭前情報人員涉嫌從事間諜活動。<span style=\"color: red;\">華為晚上發表聲明，指王偉晶因「個人原因」，涉嫌違反波蘭法律而被逮捕調查，事件對華為「全球聲譽造成了不良影響」，決定與他終止僱傭關係。</span><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美阻技術輸出　拒續批華為出口許可<br />\n<br />\n華為的聲明又重申「一直遵守業務所在國的所有適用法律法規」，「合規經營」，並要求所有員工「遵守所在國法律法規」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，在王偉晶被波蘭拘捕後，波蘭內政部長布魯丁斯基（Joachim Brudzinski）表示，歐盟與北約應該研究，定出共同立場，以決定是否讓華為的電信設備留在成員國內。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【華為危機】中國任意拘捕加國公民 杜魯多：無視外交豁免權<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n波蘭國家安全局早前向路透社表示，今次的指控是針對個人，不是指控華為直接從事間諜活動。中國外交部及駐波蘭大使館均高度關注事件，要求波蘭保障當事人合法權益。<br />\n<br />\n波蘭國家安全局發言人Stanislaw Zaryn表示，當局於本月8日將二人羈押，法院批准當局扣查二人3個月，一旦間諜罪名成立，最高可判監10年。他重申，拘捕行動是針對中國籍疑犯的個人行為，對其工作的公司不會採取任何行動。<br />\n<br />\n華為較早前的聲明，未有透露被捕者的身份，亦未對案件作出任何評論。而被羈押的波蘭前情報人員曾任職的Orange波蘭分公司則表示，波蘭國家安全局於周二曾搜集相關員工的資料，但拒絕透露員工的身份，並不清楚調查是否涉及員工的專業工作，但會配合當局調查。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190112/59133685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190112%2F59133685&d=HHoCLFOiTHifjI0VPSidX%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=803d1663\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190112%2F59133685&h=1c2620d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190112/59133685</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華為炒佢係咪間接承認佢從事間諜活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舟舟真係好  成個中國撐腰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但晶晶就做左安全套 比人用完即棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11d3b34abbe265592d1bcef30a9370f23992e42","tid":979289,"uid":76216,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T14:50:39.000Z","msg":"次元切割刀"},{"pid":"e57cba7514a7946379c10a981cd10c9412542f40","tid":979289,"uid":204803,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T14:52:03.000Z","msg":"同肥平一樣，即刻割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04f81a1506a14b5d911012a0e57d9bf1b85e35d","tid":979289,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T14:54:09.000Z","msg":"割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔爭在抑鬱自殺埋啦笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452f8e206e620778c8c85f27c6bdfb86e34c52da","tid":979289,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T14:55:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Condom</span></span>"},{"pid":"99d0abd990fa1b2c5decc2f8cdc529ae6eca0bbc","tid":979289,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T14:56:11.000Z","msg":"點解我唔係太子女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822787373b145690ba5a8aedc6f6920e40d28272","tid":979289,"uid":123082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e57cba7514a7946379c10a981cd10c9412542f40","tid":979289,"uid":204803,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime